{"tid":1256931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇反送中website？","createTime":"2019-06-25T09:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T11:01:15.000Z","uid":112405,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e93d6417f4db2009553e5c42e686e4bb69b9382a","tid":1256931,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"我地可唔可以整個網站，簡簡單單有條timeline 講述反送中一連串既事件？ 好似photo gallery咁，每張相配個caption, 方便其他人去了解。<br />\n <br />\n當然其他文宣圖,剪報就可以用另一個category放係個網頁，有一個合集就可以提供更多素材去做文宣。<br />\n<br />\n同時可以比登報團隊放個website上去，咁就有頭版draw attention, 亦可以宣傳到個網頁，比大眾睇到更多紀錄片同相。(當然d相同片都要保護到示威者，唔想有人因為呢個網而<br />\n<br />\n雖然好趕，但只要有個網站，就可以不斷update相同片。<br />\n之後有其他idea都可以再加？<br />\n<br />\n如果有人整緊，可以由個post沈。"},{"pid":"aa30928a4e7d9dadfc97ae8a99681824286f0680","tid":1256931,"uid":223727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以幫手編輯一下維基百科"},{"pid":"5d2bc4670e038e392de63f1284d68cc3e48a405b","tid":1256931,"uid":112405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"未打完就禁錯制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;d 相同片都要check過先出，唔好令相中人有任何風險&rdquo;"},{"pid":"780915a3aecf2b96295e5546572a54081701f6fa","tid":1256931,"uid":223727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E8%88%87%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cb31694d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h